at.ac.oeaw.cemm.bsf.vcffilter.excelparser

Class RecurrenceParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.oeaw.cemm.bsf.vcffilter.excelparser.Parser
      • at.ac.oeaw.cemm.bsf.vcffilter.excelparser.ExcelParser
        • at.ac.oeaw.cemm.bsf.vcffilter.excelparser.RecurrenceParser

  • public class RecurrenceParser
extends ExcelParser
    Parser for recurrence files. In its original version, it parsed xlsx formatted recurrence files. But there where issues with number precision of variant positions. Therefore, parsing is done from a tsv file, which also means that the ExcelParser functionalities are not needed right now. This may change in the future. RecurrenceParser.java 04 OCT 2016
    Since:
    1.0
